creator: Phondini Partners LLC
descriptionHtml:
FishLine finds Fresh Local Seafood for you from:
• fishermen off the boat
• local seafood markets
• farmer's markets
• local restaurants or cafes, or
• community supported fisheries

Use FishLine to find fresh local seafood anywhere on the planet for Free!

Fishermen, Markets, CSFs, and Restaurants can post their available local seafood on FishLine for Free!

CrabLine is a directory of fishermen who will take orders for crab, fish and other seafood via phone, text or email.

FishLine includes features such as using GPS to find the nearest port, boat or market with fresh seafood for sale, so if you are on vacation or are near several ports, FishLine helps you figure out where to find the fish.

If your friends don't have smart phones, they can use FishLine at FishLineApp.com

Like us on Facebook at FishLineApp, and Follow us on Twitter @FishLineApp.

FishLine includes material gathered by the Faces of California Fishing project.

FishLine is financed in part by a grant from the Central California Joint Cable/Fisheries Liaison Committee.

Interested in having FishLine for your Fishing Community? Please contact the developers Phondini Partners.
descriptionShort: FishLine for Fresh Local Sustainable Seafood, Crab & Fish with Recipes & Stories

CrabLine is a directory of fishermen who will take orders for crab, fish and other seafood via phone, text or email.

FishLine includes features such as using your location to find the nearest port, boat or market with fresh seafood for sale, so if you are on vacation or are near several ports, FishLine helps you figure out where to find the fish.

FishLine also uses your location to configure special features when you are in Rhode Island, Virginia or Hawaii.

If your friends don't have smart phones, they can use FishLine at FishLineApp.com

Like us on Facebook at FishLineApp, and Follow us on Twitter @FishLineApp.

FishLine includes material gathered by the Faces of California Fishing project.

FishLine is financed in part by a grant from the Central California Joint Cable/Fisheries Liaison Committee.

Interested in having FishLine for your Fishing Community? Please contact the developers Phondini Partners.
